  "body": "While the style guide does say to [avoid block comments](https://doc.rust-lang.org/stable/style/style/comments.html#avoid-block-comments.), they should perhaps be briefly mentioned in the \"Comments\" section of the book, to avoid leaving readers with the false belief that they don't exist.\n\nr? @steveklabnik\n",
